---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-20 py-10 border-t border-slate-800 text-slate-500 text-sm">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">BetKing.blog</h3>
                <p>Helping you find the safest crypto betting options since 2026.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-xs">
                <p><strong>Affiliate Disclosure:</strong> BetKing.blog is an independent site. We may receive commissions when you click our links and make deposits. This does not affect our reviews or your costs.</p>
                <p><strong>Responsible Gambling:</strong> Gambling can be addictive. Please play responsibly. If you need help, visit BeGambleAware.org. Must be 18+ to play.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-slate-800/50 flex justify-between items-center">
            <p>&copy; {currentYear} BetKing.blog. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="space-x-4">
                <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white">Privacy</a>
                <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-white">Terms</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>